title: My Boss Bajrangbali
subTitle: A corrupt politician kills Anji's parents and plans to demolish a temple. Later, Lord Hanuman takes human form to help Anji fight the politician.

title: Meri Zindagi Ek Agneepath
subTitle: Ramakrishna, a mechanic, is framed for the murder of his wife by his father-in-law who then takes his son away from him. Following his release, Ramakrishna sets out to find his child.

title: Super Ranga
subTitle: Ranga, a reckless thrill-seeker, falls in love with Swathi who makes him promise to be more responsible. However, she breaks up with him when he goes back to his old ways.

title: Stalin
subTitle: Stalin, a former army officer, is deeply moved by the suicide of a girl with physical disabilities. So, he devises a plan to extend unconditional help to those who need it to establish peace.

title: Garam
subTitle: Varala, a jobless young man, leaves his home to prove himself to his father. However, before achieving his goal, he falls in love with Sameera and tries to woo and save her from gangster Biju.

title: Fidaa
subTitle: An NRI medical student falls in love with a vivacious woman. However, they face challenges in their relationship due to their differences in personalities.

title: Rudhran
subTitle: A man's life takes an unexpected turn when he stumbles upon a criminal network. Determined to bring the truth to light, he sets out to expose the nefarious organisation and protect his loved ones.

title: Vivegam
subTitle: Ajay Kumar, a former counter-terrorism agent, is called for a special mission. However, he is betrayed by his friends and is accused of extremely treasonous acts.

title: Kali Kitaab
subTitle: When narratives from a cryptic book spring to life, a woman experiences bizarre phenomena and resolves to uncover the identity of its enigmatic writer.

title: Gally Rowdy
subTitle: A young man tries to find a balance between his love interest and friends. Meanwhile, his friends convince him to stay rowdy.

title: Atma Ka Khel
subTitle: A woman named Devi becomes her village's resident exorcist and tries to solve their paranormal problems by using her skills to the maximum.

title: Atma Ka Khel
subTitle: A woman named Devi becomes her village's resident exorcist and tries to solve their paranormal problems by using her skills to the maximum.

title: Bunglow No 17
subTitle: Gautham and Deeksha, along with their daughter, move into an isolated bungalow gifted to them by Gautham's father. Soon, they start experiencing paranormal activities around the house.

title: Naagin Bani Suhaagan
subTitle: Vaishali, an ardent devotee of Lord Shiva, is blessed with a boon to transform herself into a shapeshifting snake. She falls into a dilemma when circumstances force her to go against her love.

title: Target Killing
subTitle: A young NRI plans to return to his homeland and marry a woman of his parents' choice. However, confusion ensues after he fall in love with a woman during the course of the journey.

title: Secret Agent
subTitle: Forced to live a detached life in the Andaman Islands, a secret agent comes across a woman pursued by debtors and tries to protect her.

title: Main Hoon Dandadhikari
subTitle: Following his father's death, a man gives up on his dream to become a film-maker and joins the police force. He then attempts to track down a psychopathic killer who targets schoolgirls.

title: Super Khiladi Returns
subTitle: Guru hatches several plans to separate Priya and her lover Thirukumaran. However, Thirukumaran successfully manages to escape from Guru's evil plans and traps him in another problem.

title: Yashoda
subTitle: Surrogate mother Yashodha is advised to follow a few guidelines to keep herself and her baby healthy and safe. However, something happens at the surrogate centre that puts both of them at risk.

title: Inspector Vijay
subTitle: Vijay, an honest police officer, meets Samyukta at a cafe and falls in love with her. However, his life changes when he witnesses a kidnapping and ends up helping a lonely woman, Lavanya.

title: Tantra
subTitle: Rekha, a woman with the ability to perceive spirits, sees her life take a dark turn when she encounters a sinister black magic practitioner.

title: Maaveeran Kittu
subTitle: Kittu, a young man from a Dalit community, falls in love with Gomathi, a woman from an upper-caste family. However, when the villagers discover their relationship, they kill Gomathi's father and falsely accuse Kittu of the crime.

title: Maaveeran Kittu
subTitle: Kittu, a young man from a Dalit community, falls in love with Gomathi, a woman from an upper-caste family. However, when the villagers discover their relationship, they kill Gomathi's father and falsely accuse Kittu of the crime.

title: Chintu Ji
subTitle: Rishi, the son of a legendary actor, decides to enter politics and go to Hadbahedi, a remote village. However, he creates havoc by misleading the villagers who trust him simply because he is famous.

title: Chalo
subTitle: Hari and Karthika fall in love with each other but are distraught when they find they are from different castes. However, they decide to fight for their relationship and parents' approval.

title: Jigar Kaleja
subTitle: A short tempered cab driver, Raju, unwillingly becomes the saviour of a village. When an industrialist tries to drive away the villagers by polluting their water and air, Raju steps up to help them.

title: International Sabse Bada Khiladi
subTitle: A disturbing vision prompts a man to flee his impending marriage, but he soon realises that his wicked look-alike has stolen his identity.

title: Liger -- Saala Crossbreed
subTitle: A talented young MMA fighter trains hard to rise up the ranks. However, his goals are hindered when his lover is kidnapped.

title: Munjya
subTitle: When Bittu visits his village, he uncovers a dark family secret involving a vengeful spirit, Munjya, who is desperate to marry. Bittu must navigate through chaos to protect himself and his lover.

title: Yudh Ek Jung
subTitle: Chandu, a supermarket employee, encounters trouble when he decides to help Indu, an aspiring actress, and gets embroiled in a murder case.

title: Ugram
subTitle: Shiva, a reckless CI officer, often lands himself in trouble. However, his impulsive actions take a dark turn when his family goes missing from a hospital after an accident.

title: Hidimbha
subTitle: In Hyderabad, a series of murders targets young girls. Later, officers Aadhya and Abhay investigate as more victims disappear, soon discovering a common link among them.

title: Kayamkulam Kochunni
subTitle: Ill-treated since childhood by the wealthy people, Kayamkulam Kochunni decides to steal from the rich and feed the poor and the lower caste community, thus growing into a hero for the downtrodden.
